title: Ep 44: Consumerism & The Philosophy of Futility & Why Smurfs are EVIL
description: Do you have enough crap!??! NO you don't. Get a job, get to working. Make money and buy more stuff. That's what consumerism tells us. CP explores this phenomena and explains why the Smurfs are EVIL.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
